{"tid":1881604,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港府將安排免費包機　接載鑽石公主號港人回港","createTime":"2020-02-15T16:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T20:37:24.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b0fac8f2bc8c4d1d34b0025660b05001c012e9c6","tid":1881604,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:08:55.000Z","msg":"保安局表示，特區政府正安排包機免費接載在「鑽石公主號」上接受檢疫的香港居民，在獲准離船登岸後盡快返港。<br />\n<br />\n待日本當局確定具體安排，特區政府會盡快通知受影響香港居民具體的返港日期和安排。考慮到相關公共衛生風險，有關乘客抵港後會安排入住檢疫中心接受14天檢疫。"},{"pid":"da49d0cbef81eda155c5fc8034ab6c3f670f1c0c","tid":1881604,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:09:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200215/s00001/1581782721296/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200215%2Fs00001%2F1581782721296%2F&d=uD1rvIJwXfBqs1i1iclFx3hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=50584ae3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200215%2Fs00001%2F1581782721296%2F&h=ead40c04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200215/s00001/1581782721296/</a>"},{"pid":"8bbeecebfddc1a825c0b2beac4115dc68a760bd2","tid":1881604,"uid":167295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:09:31.000Z","msg":"又玩作對"},{"pid":"59b9acde08a411f65b75dbedc81defdc6be6f3b1","tid":1881604,"uid":92188,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:10:23.000Z","msg":"呢批係要接嘅"},{"pid":"cd3bf738b0f0f99af0a254658cb22d9df970b45c","tid":1881604,"uid":112622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:10:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2cef586f59f44479f979ff0b7089363eec702474","tid":1881604,"uid":40745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59b9acde08a411f65b75dbedc81defdc6be6f3b1","tid":1881604,"uid":92188,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1